item.description:
Join us for dinner and drinks at the Naked Fish in Framingham. Meet new friendly and interesting people and have fun enjoying dinner and relaxing. If you are new to our group or haven't been in a while, this is a great event to attend!

Everyone pays for their own food/drink. If you visit the Naked Fish website and sign up for the email newsletter, they will send you a coupon for a free appetizer. http://www.nakedfish....

We will meet near the hostess area. If you're late, please look for us at our table. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.

Look forward to seeing you for a fun night!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) near hostess area or at our table- please call 774 232 0000 if you have trouble finding us.
item.name: Dinner and Drinks at the Naked Fish, Framingham
